sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant SQL as SQL Warehouse
    participant UC as Unity Catalog Tables
    participant Vol as UC Volume

    User->>UI: Click "Run Extract"
    activate UI

    UI->>API: POST /api/extracts/{id}/run
    activate API

    Note over API,SQL: Initialize Run Record
    API->>SQL: INSERT INTO extract_runs<br/>(status='running', triggered_by, started_at)
    activate SQL
    SQL-->>API: run_id returned
    deactivate SQL

    Note over API,SQL: Load Extract Definition
    API->>SQL: SELECT * FROM extract_definitions WHERE id = {id}
    activate SQL
    SQL-->>API: definition (columns_config, parameters, source_table, file_format)
    deactivate SQL

    Note over API: Build Dynamic SQL
    rect rgb(214, 232, 247)
        API->>API: Parse columns_config JSON
        API->>API: Apply parameter filters & WHERE clauses
        API->>API: Construct SELECT statement with aliases
    end

    Note over API,SQL: Execute Extract Query
    API->>SQL: Execute dynamic SELECT against source table
    activate SQL
    SQL->>UC: Scan source data table (inventory_data, pos_data, etc.)
    activate UC
    UC-->>SQL: Raw rows from source table
    deactivate UC
    SQL-->>API: Result set (rows + schema)
    deactivate SQL

    Note over API: Generate Output File
    rect rgb(214, 240, 224)
        API->>API: Format rows → CSV / JSON / XLSX
        API->>API: Apply delimiter, encoding, naming template
        API->>API: Compute row_count and file_size_bytes
    end

    API->>Vol: WorkspaceClient.files.upload(path, content)
    activate Vol
    Vol-->>API: Upload confirmed (output_path)
    deactivate Vol

    Note over API,SQL: Update Run Record
    API->>SQL: UPDATE extract_runs SET<br/>status='success', row_count, file_size_bytes,<br/>output_path, completed_at WHERE id = {run_id}
    activate SQL
    SQL-->>API: Update confirmed
    deactivate SQL

    Note over API,SQL: Write Audit Entry
    API->>SQL: INSERT INTO audit_log<br/>(action='extract_run', entity_id, user_id,<br/>timestamp, details JSON)
    activate SQL
    SQL-->>API: Audit entry saved
    deactivate SQL

    API-->>UI: 200 OK { run_id, status, row_count,<br/>file_size_bytes, output_path }
    deactivate API

    UI-->>User: Toast notification<br/>"Extract complete · 42,381 rows exported"
    deactivate UI

    Note over User,UI: Dashboard auto-refreshes run history
